title: SomeNews Radio - Bets and Bond Recruitment
description: This week on the show we looked at the story of a man who lost his name in a bet, the way MI5 is looking for spies, Larry tells us about Brian Ferry's divorce and this podcast also includes a topic we didn't do in the show, "things you have had stuck in your body". We didn't put that one in the actual show. Here's the podcast of it for you to download/listen.
